classification.description: Recruitment services

tender.description: Selwood Housing and Alliance Homes are collaborating to create a four-year Framework of Recruitment Agencies to provide both temporary and permanent staff on behalf of the respective organisation. This Framework will form a crucial part of their resourcing strategy for the four years and may run alongside other initiatives. This opportunity has been divided in to 7 Lots:Lot 1: Management and professional servicesLot 2: Business Admin and Office SupportLot 3: ICTLot 4: Finance and PayrollLot 5: Housing and Community ServicesLot 6: Technical Services and DevelopmentLot 7: Board, Executive and Senior ManagementBidders can apply for one, some or all of the Lots available. For further details please review the Tender documents.
